{"tid":978695,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國會立法　確保停擺結束後公務員獲補薪","createTime":"2019-01-12T06:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T19:02:37.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0d321ca9e108d51f3eaa8a713125498b8cabb4","tid":978695,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"美國會立法　確保停擺結束後公務員獲補薪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190112/1499305/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190112%2F1499305%2F&d=9QEd1l5XEVbDM3zfQEiDxL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=d6cf6160\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190112%2F1499305%2F&h=04987f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190112/1499305/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院通過法案，確保政府局部停擺結束後，所有受影響的公務員，包括被迫放假的人，將獲補發薪水。<br />\n<br />\n參議院周四已一致通過該法案，法案將呈交總統川普簽署，預料他會簽名通過。<br />\n<br />\n約80萬名公務員在政府停擺後，被迫放無薪假或無薪工作。部份公務員昨日遊行至白宮前示威，批評總統及政客拿他們的生計作政治鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，眾議院周五亦以240-179票通過法案，讓內政部及環境保護部等一些聯邦部門結束21日停擺，但川普表明反對法案，而參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈（Mitch McConnell）則警告不會把法案提交參議院表決。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"0e5d00f2b5efed1a614b375e8cd9ec106e588d00","tid":978695,"uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔洗返工有糧出"},{"pid":"31fd7ff1b5fede65d45f32500638bf29c8405a41","tid":978695,"uid":3302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"放假有糧補返<br />\n快點停擺我"},{"pid":"97aa54bdc02b6eb29ee4c9ac2ed464859d8825b8","tid":978695,"uid":8858,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"冇汗出有糧出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"